title: mIRC 6.16 + Keygen
description: mIRC 6.16 plus a key creator. Installation and implementation of the key only takes 5 seconds. Simply start by installing the program mirc.exe (it is version 6.16, will not work with current versions) and check \\\"Launch program\\\". Then, open the file keygen.exe and put a word over 5 letters into the section, and press \\\"copy\\\". Then, when in the main IRC window in the taskbar, Help > Register IRC > Enter the word you entered in the keygen in the \\\"name\\\" section > in the key section, right click and paste. Your version of mIRC 6.16 is now registered under your name, and there will be no loss of your settings nor will there be the annoying pop-up asking you to pay.
